31d96c6b-0b8b-4750-8ee5-a1725ac27059.title: <player>
31d96c6b-0b8b-4750-8ee5-a1725ac27059.text: The chancellor trusts me. I have come for instructions.

dda4f350-1edb-4ec1-9147-4a86b93031c5.title: Osman
dda4f350-1edb-4ec1-9147-4a86b93031c5.text:
Our prince is captive by the Lady Keli. We just need
to make the rescue. There are two things we need
you to do.

options.text: What is the first thing I must do?
What is the second thing you need?

8f7ae2b6-7947-48f0-8f44-bef4d863cc6e.title: <player>
8f7ae2b6-7947-48f0-8f44-bef4d863cc6e.text: What is the first thing I must do?

53a0d1dd-5432-4150-aaf1-01d67aefc1cc.title: Osman
53a0d1dd-5432-4150-aaf1-01d67aefc1cc.text:
The prince is guarded by some stupid guards and a
clever woman. The woman is our only way to get the
prince out. Only she can walk freely about the area.

ddf96079-4cf7-4b13-90fc-e9972597e4f9.title: Osman
ddf96079-4cf7-4b13-90fc-e9972597e4f9.text:
I think you will need to tie her up. One coil of rope
should do for that. Then, disguise the prince as her to
get him out without suspicion.

f9f22a78-2c7b-4e57-931b-4402e07f2d86.title: <player>
f9f22a78-2c7b-4e57-931b-4402e07f2d86.text: How good must the disguise be?

a7be9553-1284-4068-bbd7-735caf1a7f42.title: Osman
a7be9553-1284-4068-bbd7-735caf1a7f42.text:
Only enough to fool the guards at a distance. Get a
skirt like hers. Same colour, same style. We will only
have a short time.

bde3759b-1bc9-4135-b70b-cff4238c923a.title: Osman
bde3759b-1bc9-4135-b70b-cff4238c923a.text:
Get a blonde wig, too. That is up to you to make or
find. Something to colour the skin of the prince.

748bb829-87cf-4ecf-bd4b-8e0c4ff3a409.title: Osman
748bb829-87cf-4ecf-bd4b-8e0c4ff3a409.text:
My daughter and top spy, Leela, can help you. She has
sent word that she has discovered where they are
keeping the prince.

9347469f-deeb-493b-ba88-2cc6a1508798.title: Osman
9347469f-deeb-493b-ba88-2cc6a1508798.text:
It's near Draynor Village. She is lurking somewhere
near there now.

options.text: What is the second thing you need?
Okay, I better go find some things.

451dc4d9-9055-467d-bb54-ace862bf7a36.title: <player>
451dc4d9-9055-467d-bb54-ace862bf7a36.text: Okay, I better go find some things.

88d4d58e-2362-4d9d-b6d7-ae02a314d82e.title: <player>
88d4d58e-2362-4d9d-b6d7-ae02a314d82e.text: What is the second thing you need?

5e908323-eef7-4bb1-9d94-52ca5472d325.title: Osman
5e908323-eef7-4bb1-9d94-52ca5472d325.text:
We need the key, or we need a copy made. If you can
get some soft clay then you can copy the key...

6062bc4d-01d4-4ca6-9753-9a2e1c4a9c6a.title: Osman
6062bc4d-01d4-4ca6-9753-9a2e1c4a9c6a.text:
...If you can convince Lady Keli to show it to you
for a moment. She is very boastful.
It should not be too hard.

b0f1af0e-6eae-4083-8b8d-e9bc8b36436e.title: Osman
b0f1af0e-6eae-4083-8b8d-e9bc8b36436e.text: Bring the imprint to me, with a bar of bronze.

options.text: What is the first thing I must do?
What exactly is the second thing you need?
Okay, I better go find some things.

de92df74-c800-42c2-b90a-d74d34f97ea8.title: Osman
de92df74-c800-42c2-b90a-d74d34f97ea8.text: Well done; we can make the key now.

5a1e5736-882b-4a0d-8ee6-5c1c7df96a4c.title: Osman
5a1e5736-882b-4a0d-8ee6-5c1c7df96a4c.text: Pick the key up from Leela.

7f71f60b-c9d3-4f39-a84b-60708460a582.title: <player>
7f71f60b-c9d3-4f39-a84b-60708460a582.text: Can you tell me what I still need to get?

d32cc53b-17bf-4439-ae1a-972ecbded414.title: Osman
d32cc53b-17bf-4439-ae1a-972ecbded414.text: You can collect the key from Leela.

57ec022b-a7b9-4904-9111-d1e79ac2b120.title: Osman
57ec022b-a7b9-4904-9111-d1e79ac2b120.text:
A print of the key in soft clay and a bronze bar.
 Then, collect the key from Leela.

644b8dee-0665-40cf-bdab-fbdcd6101c67.title: Osman
644b8dee-0665-40cf-bdab-fbdcd6101c67.text: The key you already have. Good.

62c53bae-7932-4e86-9b60-4846fea86f2e.title: Osman
62c53bae-7932-4e86-9b60-4846fea86f2e.text: The wig you have got; well done.

5624afc7-4fcb-4c2e-9be0-4be9fa0cbda5.title: Osman
5624afc7-4fcb-4c2e-9be0-4be9fa0cbda5.text:
You need to make a blonde wig somehow.
 Leela may help.

9bf7d1a2-5588-4bb9-9189-cd8e210a1816.title: Osman
9bf7d1a2-5588-4bb9-9189-cd8e210a1816.text: You will need a skirt that looks the same as Keli's.

9b7fb4db-aab3-44b7-a055-6662b5e84e62.title: Osman
9b7fb4db-aab3-44b7-a055-6662b5e84e62.text:
You have the skin paint; well done.
I thought you would struggle to make that.

fef97e80-6330-4e8b-abee-d983d907c403.title: Osman
fef97e80-6330-4e8b-abee-d983d907c403.text: Something to make the prince's skin appear lighter.

f5c63cd3-2543-420c-ad65-551f3a3fb556.title: Osman
f5c63cd3-2543-420c-ad65-551f3a3fb556.text: A rope with which to tie Keli up.

8da36d12-e578-4a16-9591-509e7f6be8c4.title: Osman
8da36d12-e578-4a16-9591-509e7f6be8c4.text:
Once you have everything, go to Leela. She must be
ready to get the prince away.

options.text: Thank you. I will try to find the other items.
Can you tell me what I still need to get?

f1410159-4301-410d-8725-4394b6ab62bf.title: <player>
f1410159-4301-410d-8725-4394b6ab62bf.text: Thank you. I will try to find the other items.

a51004c7-1634-4149-99c0-f148c7570994.title: Osman
a51004c7-1634-4149-99c0-f148c7570994.text:
The prince is safe and on his way home with Leela.
You can pick up your payment from the chancellor.

1a790465-5721-409d-a488-b1f99a17c242.title: Osman
1a790465-5721-409d-a488-b1f99a17c242.text:
Well done. A great rescue. I will remember you if I
have anything dangerous to do.
